==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Self-abasement
<hw>Self`-a*base"ment</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Degradation of one's self by one's own act.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Humiliation or abasement proceeding from
consciousness of inferiority, guilt, or shame.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Self-abasing</ent>⟦br⟧
